  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Concrete Truck Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>YTL CONCRETE (S) PTE. LTD.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will provide customer service by safely and efficiently transporting ready-mixed concrete from the batching plant to customer sites, operating truck controls to deliver concrete accurately, and maintaining the truck to ensure quality and safety.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive the truck safely from the batching plant to customer sites to deliver ready-mixed concrete</li><li>Operate truck levers to release concrete down the chute into wheelbarrows, other containers, or directly into the designated pouring area</li><li>Clean the truck thoroughly after each delivery using a water hose to prevent concrete from hardening inside the mixer and on the truck</li><li>Follow safety procedures to protect yourself and others during transportation and delivery</li><li>Meet delivery schedules to ensure timely service and customer satisfaction</li><li>Maintain the truck in good working condition to support efficient operations and prevent delays</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Hold a valid Class 4 License to operate the concrete delivery truck</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Eligible for trip/cartage incentive based on delivery performance</li><li>Ability to achieve annual bonus by meeting cartage targets</li></ul>",
